snippet.title: SKYE - Coming Soon Trailer
snippet.description:
SKYE is coming to Steam! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1214360/SKYE/

SKYE is a game created by students at Breda University of Applied Sciences.
Fly around a painterly island group inspired by the Scottish Hebrides.
